## TECH STACK — NON-NEGOTIABLE

- Next.js 14 with App Router (`/app` directory structure)
- TypeScript throughout — no `.js` files, only `.tsx` and `.ts`
- Tailwind CSS for all styling — no CSS modules, no styled-components
- `next/font` for font loading — no external font CDN links
- `next/image` for every image — no raw `<img>` tags, ever
- `next/link` for all internal navigation — no raw `<a>` tags for internal routes
- No `"use client"` unless strictly required (forms, interactive components only)
- Server Components by default for all pages and layouts

