### Click-to-Call
The phone number must be clickable on every page at all times on mobile.

```tsx
// Sticky mobile CTA — present on every page via layout
<a
  href="tel:+61485043175"
  className="fixed bottom-4 right-4 z-50 md:hidden bg-brand-orange text-white px-5 py-3 rounded-full font-semibold shadow-lg"
